11. Vendored Compatibility Headers
    ----------------------------
    Location:    compat/
    License:     Dual-licensed (underlying code is GPL-2.0; compat additions
                are GPL-2.0)
    Role:        Platform abstraction for modern C standards
    
    Components:
    - compat.h              — DOS→POSIX/Win32 shim macros
    - pragmas_gcc.h         — 174 portable C replacements for Watcom ASM
    - sdl_driver.c/.h       — SDL2 video/input/timer wrapper
    - audio_stub.c/.h       — Audio system stubs (DOS audio driver stub)
    - mact_stub.c           — Config parser & input stubs
    - net_socket_*.c        — Socket abstraction (POSIX/Win32 variants)
    - sha256.c/.h           — Cryptographic hash (standard implementation)
    - hud.c/.h              — HUD rendering interface
    - log_stub.h            — Logging macros
    - msvc_unistd.h         — MSVC POSIX compatibility header


